hopobject.body: I'm doing a phd in chemistry valtrex medscape To state the obvious about Woody Allen's "Blue Jasmine" before getting into the mysterious, Cate Blanchett tops anything she's done in the past with her portrait of a fallen woman who's a hoot, a horror, a heartbreaker and a wonder.
